<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EFund Content Removal Notice</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family:'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #fff; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #222831;">
<table width="100%" height="450px" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" valign="middle">
            <table class="content" width="600"
                   style="text-align: center; padding-top: 0%; border-radius: 15px; background-color: #393e46; height: 300px">
                <tr>
                    <td style="vertical-align: top; padding-top: 20px;">
                        <h1 style="font-size: 24px; color: #ffd369; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                            EFund Content Removal Notification
                        </h1>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Dear <b>@Model.UserName</b>,</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0 35px">
                            We are writing to inform you that content associated with your fundraising
                            <a href="@Model.ViewFundraisingUri" style="color: #ffd369;">@Model.ViewFundraisingUri</a>
                            has been removed following a review by our moderation team.
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0 35px 10px 35px;">
                            The content was found to be in violation of our Terms of Use, specifically under the categories:
                            <br /><b>@Model.Violations</b>
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 20px 35px;">
                            Please ensure that future content complies with our platform policies. Repeated or serious violations may result in account suspension or permanent removal.
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 25px 0 50px 0;">
                            <a href="#" style="font-size: 18px; color: #ffd369; font-weight: 500;">
                                Contact Us
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>

</html>
